Platform Tutorial 1
===================

This game is tutorial to teach keyboard input.

The source has been annotated to teach you the basics of using PixieEngine.

Directory Overview
------------------
lib           - Compiled libraries that the game includes. You won't need to touch these.
src           - The code for all the objects in the game
Documentation - Detailed explanation of methods provided by the libraries. Contains tons of code samples. 
README        - This file
pixie         - Configuration file to specify library source location and application size.

Architecture Overview
---------------------
Engine     - Manages all the game objects and running the update and draw steps.
GameObject - Represents something in the game. In our case this represents that red square.
Square     - The guy we are learning to control.

This main file sets up the engine and configures all the initial objects.

